          <h2 style="color: #2c5aa0; margin-bottom: 20px;">Welcome to MediSync, {{firstName}}!</h2>
          
          <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Thank you for registering with MediSync. To complete your registration, please verify your email address using the code below:
          </p>
          
          <div style="background: #e3f2fd; padding: 25px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 10px;">Your verification code is:</p>
            <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #2c5aa0; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">
              {{otp}}
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            ‚è∞ This code will expire in <strong>10 minutes</strong>
          </p>
          
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
            If you didn't create an account with MediSync, please ignore this email.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
